{"tid":630070,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"放假個人應該輕鬆下 但竟然驚第二日要返工","createTime":"2018-04-15T09:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T11:36:19.000Z","uid":1779,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a2ce42876db8dc2b09bfc9b12ff747cef1f5c6","tid":630070,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"一到星期日就訓到自然醒<br />\n訓醒開始倒數今日得返十幾個鐘活動時間<br />\n然後成個下晝到夜晚就倒計時<br />\n打機又好 做運動又好<br />\n得返十個鐘....八....五.....三.....<br />\n然後又要早少少訓<br />\n驚習慣咗2日自然醒 第二日會難起身<br />\n到返工就諗起個假期做過d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做咗五日野，明明係放假個人應該要放鬆吓<br />\n但個心情仲係處於緊張狀態 <br />\n個個禮拜都係咁 人都癲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2cdfc524584875e11b837fd99fc855c1513fc1","tid":630070,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=